OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FH&M starts charging        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshoppers for online returns
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Fashion giant H&M has become the latest
OL,6, retailer to charge shoppers who return 
OL,7, items bought online.                   
OL,9,FCustomers now must pay #1.99 to return 
OL,10,Fparcels either in store or online, with
OL,11,Fthe cost taken from their refund.      
OL,12,FHowever, returns are still free for H&M
OL,13,Fmembers.                               
OL,15,FRival retailers such as Zara, Boohoo,  
OL,16,FUniqlo and Next already charge for     
OL,17,Fonline returns.                        
OL,19,FAn H&M spokesperson told the BBC the   
OL,20,Fmove was introduced in the summer.     
